text: "NATO reporting names" are a system of code names for military aircraft and other equipment used by the militaries of Russia, the rest of the former Soviet Union, other former Warsaw Pact countries, and China. The system helps communications in the military which may be confusing or unknown in the western world. == References == == Other websites == * Designations of Soviet and Russian Military Aircraft and Missiles * Aerospace Web Category:Military aviation
